@d19 5
a23 7
There are several differences from linux. From bootup procedure to network
inter
face usage. Several tasks have a different approach, as with disk
management. Mo
st differences are well documented, but involves searching manpages. This
docume
nt tries to be an index of those differences.<p>
d29 3
